<template>
    <!-- src="http://rnx4.w.dedikuoti.lt:8080/api/v1/Trip/ViewTripImage?tripFileKey=CCB57DFFDF5B4A14839D9EEBEC8C3BA8"/> -->
  
    <swiper
    :slides-per-view="3"
    :space-between="50"
    @swiper="onSwiper"
    @slideChange="onSlideChange"
  >
    <swiper-slide>http://rnx4.w.dedikuoti.lt:8080/api/v1/Trip/ViewTripImage?tripFileKey=CCB57DFFDF5B4A14839D9EEBEC8C3BA8</swiper-slide>
    <swiper-slide>Slide 2</swiper-slide>
    <swiper-slide>Slide 3</swiper-slide>
    ...
  </swiper>
</template>

<script>

// Import Swiper Vue.js components
import { useSwiper  } from 'swiper/vue';

// Import Swiper styles
import 'swiper/css';


export default {
    components: {
      Swiper,
      SwiperSlide,
    },
     
  
  data() {
        return {
            tripsImages : [],
            gallery_top:''
        }
    },
    setup() {
      const swiper = useSwiper();

      return {
        swiper,
      };
    },
}




</script>

</style>
